><br><span class=\"line\">停在康桥上的那只蝴蝶</span><br><span class=\"line\">飞往午夜河畔的翡冷翠</span><br><span class=\"line\">遗憾被偶然藏在了诗页</span><br><span class=\"line\">是微笑都透不进的世界</span><br><span class=\"line\">巴黎的鳞爪 感伤的文法</span><br><span class=\"line\">要用音乐翻阅</span><br><span class=\"line\">晚风的灯下 旅人的花茶</span><br><span class=\"line\">我换成了咖啡</span><br><span class=\"line\">之后他就</span><br><span class=\"line\">爱上了苦涩这个复杂词汇</span><br><span class=\"line\">因为这才是挥手</span><br><span class=\"line\">向云彩道别的滋味</span><br><span class=\"line\">小船静静往返</span><br><span class=\"line\">马谛斯的海岸</span><br><span class=\"line\">星空下的夜晚</span><br><span class=\"line\">交给梵谷点燃</span><br><span class=\"line\">梦美的太短暂</span><br><span class=\"line\">孟克桥上呐喊</span><br><span class=\"line\">这世上的热闹</span><br><span class=\"line\">出自孤单</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><strong>都看到这儿了，不如关注每日推送的“科文路”、互动起来~</strong></p>\n<p><strong>至少点个赞再走吧~</strong></p>","categories":[{"name":"人文","path":"api/categories/人文.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"人文","path":"api/tags/人文.json"},{"name":"荐歌","path":"api/tags/荐歌.json"}]}